@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081
@internalSecret = my-order-internal-secret-key-2026

### ── 수동 변수 설정 (응답 핸들러 안 될 때 복사해서 붙여넣기) ──
@memberId =
@accessToken =
@refreshToken =
@adminMemberId =
@adminAccessToken =
@addressId =


### ════════════════════════════════════════
###  STEP 1. 회원가입 / 로그인 (Auth API)
###
###  ★ ADMIN 계정은 서비스 기동 시 자동 시딩
###    (ADMIN_EMAIL/ADMIN_PASSWORD 환경변수)
### ════════════════════════════════════════

### STEP 1-1. 회원가입
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@test.com",
  "password": "Test1234!@",
  "name": "테스트유저",
  "phone": "01012345678"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("memberId", response.body.data.memberId);
  client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
  client.global.set("refreshToken", response.body.data.refreshToken);
%}


### STEP 1-2. 로그인
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@test.com",
  "password": "Test1234!@"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("memberId", response.body.data.memberId);
  client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
  client.global.set("refreshToken", response.body.data.refreshToken);
%}


### STEP 1-3. ADMIN 로그인 (서비스 기동 시 자동 시딩된 계정)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@bookcommerce.com",
  "password": "Admin1234!"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("adminMemberId", response.body.data.memberId);
  client.global.set("adminAccessToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}


### STEP 1-4. 토큰 재발급
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
  client.global.set("refreshToken", response.body.data.refreshToken);
%}


### STEP 1-5. 로그아웃
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}


### ════════════════════════════════════════
###  STEP 2. 회원 정보 (Member API)
### ════════════════════════════════════════

### STEP 2-1. 내 정보 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/member/me
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER


### STEP 2-2. 내 정보 수정
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/member/me
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER

{
  "name": "수정된이름",
  "phone": "01088887777"
}


### STEP 2-3. 예치금 잔액 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/member/me/deposit
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER


### STEP 2-4. 회원 탈퇴 (주의: 실행 시 계정 비활성화)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/member/me
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "password": "Test1234!@"
}


### ════════════════════════════════════════
###  STEP 3. 배송지 관리 (Address API)
### ════════════════════════════════════════

### STEP 3-1. 배송지 등록
POST {{baseUrl}}/member/address
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER

{
  "recipient": "홍길동",
  "phone": "01012345678",
  "zipcode": "06236",
  "address1": "서울특별시 강남구 테헤란로 1",
  "address2": "101동 1001호",
  "isDefault": true
}

> {%
  client.global.set("addressId", response.body.data.addressId);
%}


### STEP 3-2. 배송지 목록 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/member/address
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER


### STEP 3-3. 배송지 수정
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/member/address/{{addressId}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER

{
  "recipient": "김길동",
  "address2": "202호",
  "isDefault": false
}


### STEP 3-4. 배송지 삭제
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/member/address/{{addressId}}
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER


### ════════════════════════════════════════
###  STEP 4. 판매자 등록 / 승인 (Seller API)
### ════════════════════════════════════════

### STEP 4-1. 판매자 등록 신청
POST {{baseUrl}}/member/seller
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER
X-Email-Verified: true

{
  "shopName": "테스트서점",
  "businessNumber": "1234567890",
  "bankCode": "004",
  "bankAccount": "123456789012",
  "accountHolder": "홍길동"
}


### STEP 4-2. 판매자 정보 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/member/seller/{{memberId}}


### STEP 4-3. 판매자 승인 (ADMIN)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/member/admin/seller/{{memberId}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{adminMemberId}}
X-Role: ADMIN
X-Email-Verified: true

{
  "status": "APPROVED"
}


### STEP 4-4. 승인 후 판매자 정보 재조회 (status: APPROVED, role: SELLER)
GET {{baseUrl}}/member/seller/{{memberId}}


### ════════════════════════════════════════
###  STEP 5. Internal API (서비스 간 통신)
### ════════════════════════════════════════

### STEP 5-1. 회원 배송지 조회 (order-service용)
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/member/{{memberId}}/address
X-Internal-Secret: {{internalSecret}}


### STEP 5-2. 회원 활성 상태 확인 (order/payment용)
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/member/{{memberId}}/active
X-Internal-Secret: {{internalSecret}}


### STEP 5-3. 예치금 잔액 조회 (payment용)
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/member/{{memberId}}/deposit
X-Internal-Secret: {{internalSecret}}


### STEP 5-4. 예치금 충전 (transactionId 포함)
POST {{baseUrl}}/internal/member/{{memberId}}/deposit/charge
Content-Type: application/json
X-Internal-Secret: {{internalSecret}}

{
  "amount": 50000,
  "transactionId": "charge-test-001"
}


### STEP 5-5. 예치금 충전 멱등성 확인 (동일 transactionId 재요청 → 이전 결과 반환)
POST {{baseUrl}}/internal/member/{{memberId}}/deposit/charge
Content-Type: application/json
X-Internal-Secret: {{internalSecret}}

{
  "amount": 50000,
  "transactionId": "charge-test-001"
}


### STEP 5-6. 예치금 차감 (transactionId 포함)
POST {{baseUrl}}/internal/member/{{memberId}}/deposit/deduct
Content-Type: application/json
X-Internal-Secret: {{internalSecret}}

{
  "amount": 10000,
  "transactionId": "deduct-test-001"
}


### STEP 5-7. 예치금 차감 멱등성 확인 (동일 transactionId 재요청 → 이전 결과 반환, 이중 차감 안 됨)
POST {{baseUrl}}/internal/member/{{memberId}}/deposit/deduct
Content-Type: application/json
X-Internal-Secret: {{internalSecret}}

{
  "amount": 10000,
  "transactionId": "deduct-test-001"
}


### STEP 5-8. 잔액 확인 (기대: 50000 - 10000 = 40000, 멱등성으로 1회만 차감)
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/member/{{memberId}}/deposit
X-Internal-Secret: {{internalSecret}}


### STEP 5-9. 판매자 승인 여부 확인 (product-service용)
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/seller/{{memberId}}/approved
X-Internal-Secret: {{internalSecret}}


### STEP 5-10. 판매자 정산 계좌 조회 (settlement용)
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/seller/{{memberId}}/account
X-Internal-Secret: {{internalSecret}}


### STEP 5-11. 토큰 블랙리스트 확인 (gateway용)
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/token-blacklist/test-jti-value
X-Internal-Secret: {{internalSecret}}


### ════════════════════════════════════════
###  실패 케이스
### ════════════════════════════════════════

### [실패] 중복 이메일 회원가입 → 409
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@test.com",
  "password": "Test1234!@",
  "name": "중복유저",
  "phone": "01011111111"
}


### [실패] 잘못된 비밀번호 로그인 → 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@test.com",
  "password": "WrongPass1!@"
}


### [실패] 비밀번호 복잡도 미충족 → 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "weak@test.com",
  "password": "12345678",
  "name": "약한비번",
  "phone": "01033333333"
}


### [실패] 인증 없이 내 정보 조회 → 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/member/me


### [실패] 배송지 필수값 누락 → 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/member/address
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER

{
  "recipient": "",
  "phone": "",
  "zipcode": "",
  "address1": ""
}


### [실패] 존재하지 않는 배송지 삭제 → 404
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/member/address/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER


### [실패] 판매자 중복 신청 → 409
POST {{baseUrl}}/member/seller
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER
X-Email-Verified: true

{
  "shopName": "중복서점",
  "businessNumber": "9999999999",
  "bankCode": "004",
  "bankAccount": "999999999999",
  "accountHolder": "김중복"
}


### [실패] USER가 판매자 승인 시도 → 403
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/member/admin/seller/{{memberId}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{memberId}}
X-Role: USER

{
  "status": "APPROVED"
}


### [실패] 존재하지 않는 판매자 승인 → 404
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/member/admin/seller/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{adminMemberId}}
X-Role: ADMIN

{
  "status": "APPROVED"
}


### [실패] Internal API 시크릿 없이 접근 → 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/member/{{memberId}}/active


### [실패] Internal API 잘못된 시크릿 → 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/member/{{memberId}}/active
X-Internal-Secret: wrong-secret


### [실패] 잔액 부족 차감 → 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/internal/member/{{memberId}}/deposit/deduct
Content-Type: application/json
X-Internal-Secret: {{internalSecret}}

{
  "amount": 999999,
  "transactionId": "deduct-fail-001"
}


### [실패] transactionId 누락 → 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/internal/member/{{memberId}}/deposit/deduct
Content-Type: application/json
X-Internal-Secret: {{internalSecret}}

{
  "amount": 10000
}
